Class Transcript

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.jivesoftware.smack.packet.Element, org.jivesoftware.smack.packet.Packet, org.jivesoftware.smack.packet.TopLevelStreamElement

    public class Transcript
extends org.jivesoftware.smack.packet.IQ
    Represents the conversation transcript that occured in a group chat room between an Agent and a user that requested assistance. The transcript contains all the Messages that were sent to the room as well as the sent presences.
